<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7587> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7587" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Senator by 74. He was not, as I suggested in MRR 2.489, and Index, 544, a Cornelius Lentulus, since the names Caudina, Caudenius, and Caudinus are attested (Wiseman, NM 223, no. 111; Gruen, LGRR 202, note 155; Shackleton Bailey, Studies 25).\n" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/6852> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #6852" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/4> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Senator in 74, juror in the trial of Oppianicus (Cic. Cluent. 107). The full name may have been C. Cornelius Lentulus Caudinus. See RE, s. v. \"Cornelius,\" nos. 210-214." .
